Package bauernhof.preset.card

Class GCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • sag.elements.GElement
      • sag.elements.GGroup
        • bauernhof.preset.card.GCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<GElement>, Drawable
    public class GCard
extends GGroup
    A drawable card.

    Can be drawn by creating a layer using SAGPanel.addLayer(LayerPosition) and adding to it (or a GGroup child of that layer) the GCard via GGroup.addChild(sag.elements.Drawable).
    Further information can be found in the SAG documentation or in the README of the SAG Repo.
